s like Banford's got it all.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-13-test-3-part-1-2023-03-20-11-13-45/47.mp3","time_start":171.68,"time_end":173.88},{"position":48,"content":"Yes! We're really lucky.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-13-test-3-part-1-2023-03-20-11-13-45/48.mp3","time_start":173.88,"time_end":176.71},{"position":49,"content":"There are lots of really good aspects to living here.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-13-test-3-part-1-2023-03-20-11-13-45/49.mp3","time_start":176.85,"time_end":181.25},{"position":50,"content":"The schools are good","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-13-test-3-part-1-2023-03-20-11-13-45/50.mp3","time_start":181.59,"time_end":183.25},{"position":51,"content":"and the hospital here is one of the best in the country.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-13-test-3-part-1-2023-03-20-11-13-45/51.mp3","time_start":183.25,"time_end":188.25},{"position":52,"content":"Everyone I know who's been there's had a positive experience.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-13-test-3-part-1-2023-03-20-11-13-45/52.mp3","time_start":188.83,"time_end":194.27},{"position":53,"content":"Oh, I can give you the name of my dentist too in Bridge Street,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-13-test-3-part-1-2023-03-20-11-13-45/53.mp3","time_start":194.69,"time_end":201.49},{"position":54,"content":"if you're interested.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-13-test-3-part-1-2023-03-20-11-13-45/54.mp3","time_start":201.49,"time_end":203.24},{"position":55,"content":"I've been going to him for years and I've never had any problems.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/ielts-listening/ielts-cambridge-